            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "> What about exposing some internal functions that power `vim.lsp.buf.document_symbol()` and `vim.lsp.buf.workspace_symbol()` so we can get this for free?\n\nI prefer LSP too because it allows us to obtain symbols _imported_ by a particular file/buffer, whereas Treesitter doesn't provide much information beyond the single file it parses.",
