        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "> > It doesn't seem like a good idea to hardcode a particular text representation.\n> \n> We can easily add a parameter for that. Doesn't need to block an initial \"best effort\" approach. That gives a skeleton which can be improved over time, instead of sitting around waiting for perfection.\n\nWhat the motivation for doing something so new and underdeveloped directly in core? This definitely should be the job of third party plugins to innovate this space. Our job should just to provide basic primitives that aren't already available.",
